## Vulnerable Configuration

```bash
# Check current scan configuration
aws ecr describe-repositories \
    --repository-names webapp \
    --query 'repositories[0].imageScanningConfiguration'

# Simulated output:
# {
#     "scanOnPush": false
# }

# Check for lifecycle policy
aws ecr get-lifecycle-policy --repository-name webapp
# An error occurred (LifecyclePolicyNotFoundException): ...
# Lifecycle policy does not exist for the repository

# Check how many unscanned images exist
aws ecr describe-images --repository-name webapp \
    --query 'length(imageDetails[?imageScanStatus==`null`])'
# 47
# 47 images have never been scanned
```

