## Basic vs Enhanced Scanning

| Feature | Basic (Clair) | Enhanced (Inspector) |
|---------|--------------|---------------------|
| OS packages | Yes | Yes |
| Application deps (npm, pip) | No | Yes |
| Continuous re-scan | No — push only | Yes — rescans when new CVEs published |
| Integration | ECR native | Amazon Inspector service |
| Cost | Free | Inspector pricing |

For production workloads, Enhanced scanning is the correct choice. Basic scanning misses the application-level CVEs that are often the most exploitable.

